{"tid":302160,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【年度宣傳】搖頭又尾擺，HKU Enf境界","createTime":"2017-06-29T07:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T16:41:57.000Z","uid":36383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ab0dc28d1fc237b25b941c32abe420d4cb1eb2b0","tid":302160,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T07:35:09.000Z","msg":"就黎放榜啦，Jupas嘅同學仔有冇考慮過JS6767呢？（Bachelor of Economics / Bachelor of Economics and Finance）<br />\n<br />\n每年都有大約400人將HKU EnF放落band A，而每年都收125人。只要你將HKU EnF放落band A，就有1/4機會收你。HKU EnF嘅優勢在於自由嘅Double major同埋數學要求，唔計BBA(ECON)/Shitty EnF，HKU EnF應該係數學要求最低。<br />\n對DSE要求：英文至少4，數學至少3。<br />\n<br />\nEcon會用公式同埋graph去分析人嘅唔同選擇。你又知唔知中學讀過嘅AD-AS model，其實仲有個IS LM model？<br />\n<img src=\"http://learneconomicsonline.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/mundelltobin2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flearneconomicsonline.com%2Fblog%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F09%2Fmundelltobin2.png&h=2eec1859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利率點樣影響general price level同埋real output？見到咁得意嘅topic又點可以唔讀Econ？！<br />\n<br />\n相信大家都聽過囚犯困局，可曾想過如果囚犯困局重覆1000次會點樣？中國歷史《史記》所記載嘅田忌賽馬，用上馬/中馬/下馬出賽其實蘊涵住game theory。想知多d就要將HKU EnF放上A1啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n &ldquo;忌數與齊諸公子馳逐重射。孫子見其馬足不甚相遠，馬有上、中、下輩。於是孫子謂田忌曰：「君弟重射，臣能令君勝。」田忌信然之，與王及諸公子逐射千金。乃臨質，孫子曰：「今以君之下駟與彼上駟，取君上駟與彼中駟，取君中駟與彼下駟。」既馳三輩畢，而田忌一不勝而再勝，卒得王千金。<br />\n<br />\n《史記‧孫子吳起列傳》&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mylamson.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/94651941651.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mylamson.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F11%2F94651941651.jpg&h=fb2553d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係外國，讀Econ嘅人智商平均係高過讀BBA架！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/275114/1?post=2f095d02d632687209488276bf1636b17fb8177e&amp;highlight=1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/275114/1?post=2f095d02d632687209488276bf1636b17fb8177e&amp;highlight=1</a><br />\n<br />\n注意：圖上網搵，可能有錯/唔完整"},{"pid":"0ee75cda6041d72c01298482097fac6f9c8ee5f2","tid":302160,"uid":4238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T07:40:30.000Z","msg":"Econ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c59b871957242ae5922c6b8d53e21d337a729e9","tid":302160,"uid":6132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T07:42:08.000Z","msg":"Bba弱智先讀，以為讀完就賺大錢"},{"pid":"7195bf84599a0d0103a2d36e4a148f46bf2e34a9","tid":302160,"uid":107686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T07:52:43.000Z","msg":"cu 同 kongu 人都出手la <br />\nUST 人仲唔快D 開始水人入UST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f1441e8ac052414accfdec8dc431ffcd794bc9","tid":302160,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T10:47:31.000Z","msg":"其實你覺得有咩好過其他兩間(cu, ust)<br />\n<br />\n純八卦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a1f249f523f50c08f29b4180bc2b04a12f9bc6","tid":302160,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T10:48:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你覺得有咩好過其他兩間(cu, ust)<br />\n<br />\n純八卦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBecoz HKU <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e500b844a07564c6af1d64bc25f163b0f7c5546","tid":302160,"uid":12591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:14:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實你覺得有咩好過其他兩間(cu, ust)<br />\n<br />\n純八卦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBecoz HKU <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出街同人講一句 I'm from HKU<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" clas